thread.title: Tamara

author: Tamara
title: Tamara
text:
I decided to use buyMyplace after friends successfully sold their home. The process was very simple and easy and there were no hidden fees.
I found the packages to be great value for money and what you see is really what you get.
Being in charge of the sale of my home, the listings, dealing with potential buyers and the viewings was all arranged at a convenient time for myself which was extremely handy.
I would definitely recommend buyMyplace to anyone else looking to sell their home.
